longBusinessSummary: Kaival Brands Innovations Group, Inc. distributes electronic nicotine delivery systems (ENDS Products) and related components in the Unites States. The company offers Bidi Stick, a disposable and tamper-resistant ENDS Product in various flavor options; and Bidi Pouch, a tobacco-free nicotine formulation, which contains natural fibers and a chew-base filler in different flavors. It sells its products to retail and non-retail customers through website bidivapor.com. The company was formerly known as Quick Start Holdings, Inc. and changed its name to Kaival Brands Innovations Group, Inc. in July 2019. The company is based in Grant-Valkaria, Florida. Kaival Brands Innovations Group, Inc. is a subsidiary of Kaival Holdings, LLC.
